Package: pinba-engine-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Pinba MySQL Storage Engine — common files
 Pinba is a MySQL storage engine used to collect and analyze PHP runtime
 statistics sent over UDP by the Pinba PHP extension.
 .
 This package contains shared data files: SQL schema for default tables
 and documentation.

Package: pinba-engine-mysql-8.0
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, pinba-engine-common
Recommends: mysql-server-8.0 | mysql-community-server-8.0
Description: Pinba MySQL Storage Engine — MySQL 8.0
 Pinba is a MySQL storage engine used to collect and analyze PHP runtime
 statistics sent over UDP by the Pinba PHP extension.
 .
 This package contains ha_pinba.so compiled against MySQL 8.0 server headers.
 Install this package if you run MySQL 8.0.
 .
 After installation, activate the plugin in MySQL:
   INSTALL PLUGIN pinba SONAME 'ha_pinba.so';
 Then create the default tables:
   SOURCE /usr/share/pinba_engine/default_tables.sql

